channel.title: Pixelmc.net Cracked/prem 1.4.5 PVP Server
channel.description:
[color=maroon][font=arial black][size=18pt]Pixelmc.net is a hardcore Clan pvp server, we offer a lot to do on our server! We have minigames such as Survival Games, Jobs mcmmo, Droppartys every day, War, CTF, Spleef and more to come! We have tried to make it fairly easy to survive, so you can spend more time enjoying pvp and Clan. We have a nice staff, good hosting (No Lagg)! We hope you come out and play with us! You will not regret it![/size]
[size=14pt]Website: pixelmc.enjin.com[/size]
Server owner: jacob_day

Sorry for the video Was my first Very Great server looking for new Mature Mods, advertisers , ops, Cleaners And much more.
[size=14pt]Apply for an open Rank On the Website Enjoy your stay. [/size]
[IMG]http://i1009.photobucket.com/albums/af218/BentNBloody/Dragun3.png[/img]
[size=24pt]Secret island full of treasures Have fun [/size]
